### Two-column layout
```tsx
style={{
  display: "flex",
  justifyContent: "space-between",
  alignItems: "center",
}}
```

### Center content
```tsx
style={{
  display: "flex",
  justifyContent: "center",
  alignItems: "center",
}}
```

### Stack with gap
```tsx
style={{
  display: "flex",
  flexDirection: "column",
  gap: spacing[4],
}}
